            <tr><td style="padding:8px"><b style="color:var(--accent)">Tính từ dài</b></td><td style="padding:8px">more/less <b>and</b> more/less + adj</td><td style="padding:8px;color:var(--text-soft)"><i>She is more and more attractive.</i></td></tr>
